<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥbyby ạ̉yạ mn lạ̉jly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥbyby ạ̉yạ mn lạ̉jly jrḥt .. wʿny dẖbḥt bạ̉ydy ạlkẖṭạẗ
 ạ̉rạk ḥbyby bdẖnby ṣlbt .. wkạ̉sy sẖrbt wạ̉nt ạlạ̹lh
 ậrạk ḥsbt mʿ ạlậtẖmyn .. wtạjuⁿ mn ạlsẖwk fwq ạljbyn
 wlṣuⁿ ysạraⁿạ wlṣuⁿ ymyn .. wạ̉ṣwạt jnd lk qạỷlyn
 (ltnj ạ̹dẖạ knt ạ̉nt ạlạ̹lh)3
 2- hwạnaⁿạ wʿạraⁿạ wmraⁿạ sqwk .. wlm yʿrfwk wlm yʿlmwạ
 bạ̉nk mn ạ̉jlhm qd ạ̉tyt .. lhm wạrtḍyt bmạ qdmwạ
 wạ̉nk mn ạ̉jl kl ạlạ̉nạm .. bṣbriⁿ tḥmlt kl ạlậlạm
 wdẖqt ạlʿdẖạb wmr ạlsqạm .. ḥbyby lky tmḥw ʿny ạlậtẖạm
 (tjrʿt kạ̉sy wạ̉nt ạlạ̹lh)3
 3- ḥbyby wạ̉nt ạldẖy mạ fʿlt .. rdyaⁿạ jʿlt lạ̉jly rdy
 ksẖạẗiⁿ tsạq ạ̹ly̱ ạldẖbḥ srt .. wkạllṣ ṣrt ạ̉yạ sydy
 fyạ lyã mn ậtẖmiⁿ mʿtdy .. wyạ lk mn gẖạfriⁿ mftdy
 tudq ydạh fdạʾ ydy .. fmạdẖạ ạ̉rd lk sydy
 wạ̉nt ạlʿly wạ̉nt ạlạ̹lh
 (lk ạlqlb ạ̉hdyh ṭwl ạlḥyạẗ)2</lyrics>
